steps.name: I set the location of the device to "SWEDEN_20888"
I mock the location of the device to "SWEDEN_20888"
I click on "ACCOUNT" button
I check that the "Account Screen" is displayed
I click on "BUILD NUMBER" tab
I click on "SET LOCATION" button
I enter the location data of the "SWEDEN_20888" station
I check "Set Location" page is visible
I enter the site ID "SWEDEN_20888" in the input
I click on "SET LOCATION" button
I click on "Car Wash" advertisement
I check if "Car Wash" advertisement is displayed
I close and open application
I make sure that the location is set correctly
I check that the "Home Screen" is displayed
I click on "STORES" button
I check that the "Stores Screen" is displayed
I click on "SEARCH BAR" input
I click on "USE YOUR CURRENT LOCATION" button
I click on "SEARCH BAR FILTER" button
I check that the "Filters List Screen" is displayed
I scroll the screen "DOWN" until the "KFREEZE" filter appears and click on it
I click on "APPLY FILTERS" button
I check that the "No stores found" toast message is displayed
I click on "Arrow on top" CTA
I click on Show stores in this area button
